title: [Icemule, Bootlegger's Alley]
description: Short, sturdy buildings and multi-colored kiosks line both sides of the cobblestone alley here, under the protective south wall of Icemule Trace.  Passing merchants laden with goods of all shapes and sizes wander out of the alley towards Honeybeer Road on various errands.
